					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I bet your code isn't executed with the screen shut off. It needs to either be within natural Vblank (NMI is fired on the start of this), or in a forced Vblank. So for a quick fix, write:
<br />
<br />lda #$00
<br />sta $2001
<br />
<br />before your updating code is executed. Then afterwards, turn the screen back on with whatever settings you had before.
<br />
<br />EDIT: Try Tepple's Name Table Editor, too. This works on XP.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/" class="postlink">-Owner of Poultry Games</a></div>
