						<div class="postbody">I think if you click on tepples' "www" it should take you to his site, where I think you can download it. For some reason, it's not listed under the tools though...
<br />
<br />Your flickering is caused by shutting the screen off, I think. If you execute the code during Vblank, and make sure it takes less than ~2200 cycles, there shouldn't be any flickering.</div>

					
